overview: Nirvana Recorded Live at the Paradiso in Amsterdam, on November 25th 1991.  Drain You, Aneurysm, School, Floyd the Barber, Smells Like Teen Spirit, About a Girl, Polly, Lithium, Sliver, Breed, Come as You Are, Been a Son, Negative Creep, On a Plain, Blew, Love Buzz, Territorial Pissings
title: Nirvana Live at the Paradiso
